[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0922","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0922.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1076","title":"Apple MacOS 9 空闲锁定安全绕过漏洞","description":"MacOS 9 的空闲锁定功能存在安全绕过漏洞。本地攻击者可通过以下步骤绕过已锁定会话的密码保护：在锁定状态下选择\"注销\"选项，当系统弹出应用程序确认对话框时选择\"取消\"按钮，即可直接返回被锁定的会话界面，从而获取未授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 MacOS 9 系统，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1076"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.277","remediation":"Mac OS 9 已停止技术支持，Apple 未发布官方补丁。建议禁用系统内置空闲锁定功能，改用第三方屏幕锁定软件（如 MacBouncer Plus）替代；同时加强物理访问控制，限制本地用户接触终端，并考虑升级到受支持的 macOS 版本以获取完整安全功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94096348604173&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/745","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6e17eb087fb437c23db93be0dd8d10804be51087/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1076","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1076.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-54c2-phxc-2hgx/GHSA-54c2-phxc-2hgx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/745/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_bypass.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ec3be0baed1eb129c466b944014a0769e187fd54/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0922.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0672","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0672.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0881","title":"Falcon Web Server 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Falcon Web Server 在处理请求路径时未正确校验目录遍历序列，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 中注入“../”等点点路径穿越组件，绕过文档根目录限制读取服务器上任意文件。攻击无需身份认证，在网络可达且服务对外提供 Web 访问时即可实施，可能导致配置文件、凭据或敏感业务数据泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0881"],"sources":["epss","nvd","cve"],"published":"1999-10-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"停用或替换存在缺陷的 Falcon Web Server；若必须继续使用，应在前置反向代理或 Web 应用防火墙中拦截含“../”的路径穿越请求，限制进程用户权限与可读目录范围，并尽快迁移至已修复路径规范化的替代 Web 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T20:04:26.766757960+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0881","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/743","http://www.osvdb.org/1127"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0672.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1111","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0883","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9046,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10791}}","description":"Zeus Web Server 的搜索功能存在任意文件读取漏洞。该服务允许用户通过搜索引擎接口传入文件名参数，但未对用户输入的文件路径进行合法性校验与访问限制，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过构造特制请求，将任意文件（如配置文件、密码文件等敏感内容）的路径作为搜索选项提交给服务器，从而越权读取目标系统上的任意文件内容。此漏洞影响运行 Zeus Web Server 的受影响版本，攻击仅需通过网络向目标服务器发送恶意 HTTP 请求即可触发，无需登录凭据，危害性高，可导致服务器敏感信息泄露。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0883"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.327","remediation":"建议升级至 Zeus Web Server 3.3d 或更高版本以修复该任意文件读取漏洞，相关补丁详情可参考 Zeus Technology 官方安全公告 (http://www.zeus.com/products/ws/advisories)。如无法立即升级，可在 Zeus 配置文件 zeus.conf 中禁用搜索引擎功能，将 SearchEngine 指令设置为 off 并重启服务；同时在防火墙或反向代理层限制对搜索引擎相关 URL 路径的访问，仅允许可信 IP 访问管理端口，防止外部攻击者利用搜索选项读取服务器敏感文件。对于已停更的 Zeus Web Server，建议迁移至现代 Web 服务器（如 Nginx 或 Apache）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1126","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/742","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3380","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5546763f2cbf8b9d0a5bd1b009f21d50c3edeb8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0883.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0883","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0883.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/aeda8c7b429aa1dfdb16de3b1ae154a7b870f9be/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0883.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5w39-4f7v-wh5j/GHSA-5w39-4f7v-wh5j.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0883.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8382c78b-1155-4737-bda3-8049e968e839.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000832.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/9f009125ab2c1b8dfc814bc96f504812b3f7d59f/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0944","title":"IBM WebSphere ikeyman 弱加密密码漏洞","description":"IBM WebSphere 2.0 和 3.0 版本中的 ikeyman 工具使用弱加密算法存储 SSL 连接密钥数据库的密码，攻击者可通过分析加密后的密码文件，利用弱加密的脆弱性还原出明文密码，从而获取密钥数据库的访问权限。该漏洞影响 IBM WebSphere 2.0 及 3.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本或采用强加密方式存储密钥数据库密码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0944"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.783","remediation":"升级到 IBM WebSphere 4.0 或更高版本，该版本已弃用 ikeyman 工具并改用更安全的密钥库管理方式。如无法升级，应避免使用 ikeyman 存储 SSL 密钥库密码，改用 keytool 等工具手动管理密钥库，并对密钥库文件设置严格的文件系统权限（仅允许管理员访问）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0944","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20274","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0944.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0944","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0944.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0944.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6mpp-2p9c-58q8/GHSA-6mpp-2p9c-58q8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0944.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1763/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1406.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0701","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0701.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0902","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9036,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10781}}","description":"CVE-1999-0902 是 NIS（网络信息服务）服务端程序 ypserv 存在的一个权限控制缺陷。该漏洞的原理是 ypserv 在处理 NIS 密码表（如 passwd）相关操作时，未能对本地用户的操作权限进行严格校验，导致具有本地系统管理员（root 或等效权限）身份的用户可以绕过正常的管理流程，直接修改或篡改 NIS 域内的密码表数据。其影响范围为部署了 ypserv 提供 NIS 服务的类 Unix 系统（如 Solaris、Linux 等使用 NIS 进行集中账号管理的服务器），攻击条件要求攻击者已获得目标主机的本地管理员权限，利用方式是本地管理员借助该缺陷直接读写 NIS 密码映射表，从而可伪造或重置其他用户的凭据，破坏账号系统的完整性与安全性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0902"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:17.677","remediation":"建议升级到包含修复的 ypserv 新版本（如 2.3 及以上，随系统发行版安全更新发布）。在无法立即升级时，限制 ypserv 守护进程仅监听受信任的内部网络接口，通过防火墙规则（如 iptables）禁止非授权主机访问 111 端口及 NIS 端口范围，并收紧本地管理员权限、启用 NIS 主从同步校验以降低被篡改密码表的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0902","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0902.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0902","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0902.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0902.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r774-h43h-88gg/GHSA-r774-h43h-88gg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0902.json","https://github.com/microsoft/AzureLinuxVulnerabilityData/blob/c677135c5a44ecff201a46de647ea5bfab7c1598/osv/AZL-7456.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19991027.data","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4dd129e1-1deb-4829-a342-fdffb82aeae6.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0701.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0699","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0699.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0901","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9101,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10782}}","description":"ypserv（NIS 网络信息服务服务器端程序）存在访问控制缺陷，本地已认证用户可绕过权限检查，直接修改其他用户的 GECOS 字段（用户描述信息）及登录 Shell。该漏洞影响运行 ypserv 的 NIS 域环境，攻击前提是攻击者在目标系统上拥有合法本地账户。利用方式上，本地用户通过调用相关 NIS 服务接口即可篡改其他账号信息，进而可能提升权限或实施进一步入侵，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0901"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:17.567","remediation":"升级 ypserv 至已修复版本（NIS 服务软件包最新版），并正确配置 /var/yp/securenets 文件限制可访问的客户端网段。同时启用 ypserv 访问控制，仅允许受信任主机绑定 NIS 域；对无需 NIS 的主机应停用并卸载 ypserv 服务，加固本地用户对 GECOS 及登录 shell 的修改权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0901","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0901.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0901.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0901","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0901.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0901.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f3vg-8384-p37m/GHSA-f3vg-8384-p37m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0901.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0699.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0698","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0698.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0900","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9117,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10805}}","description":"rpc.yppasswdd（NIS 口令更新守护进程）在处理口令修改请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该进程在生成 MD5 哈希的过程中未对用户输入的长度进行边界校验，导致本地用户可通过构造超长的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖相邻内存并篡改执行流程，最终以 root 权限执行任意指令实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 NIS/yp 服务且启用了 rpc.yppasswdd 的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者需具备目标系统的本地登录权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级为高危。修复建议升级至已修补的相关系统版本或停止不必要的 rpc.yppasswdd 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0900"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:17.437","remediation":"建议升级 rpc.yppasswdd（NIS/yp-tools 或 ypserv 软件包）到厂商发布的已修复版本，例如通过操作系统包管理器执行 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade ypserv 或 yum update ypserv 安装最新补丁。如无法立即升级，应停用 yppasswdd 服务（关闭 rpc.yppasswdd 守护进程）并限制对 NIS 端口的本地访问，避免本地用户利用 MD5 哈希生成触发缓冲区溢出提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0900","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0900.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0900","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0900.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0900.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hw9r-5hfp-j23w/GHSA-hw9r-5hfp-j23w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0900.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83043/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19991027.data","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a044a934-29dc-4652-a72c-0ff2c6ac9a47.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0698.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1409","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0951","title":"Omnicron OmniHTTPd Pro 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Omnicron OmniHTTPd 1.1 及 2.4 Pro 版本的 CGI 程序 imagemap.exe 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在服务器上以 Web 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 OmniHTTPd 1.1 和 2.4 Pro 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0951"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.620","remediation":"OmniHTTPd 1.1/2.4 Pro 已停止维护且无官方补丁，建议立即停止使用该软件并迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache、Nginx、IIS）。如无法立即替换，应将服务器置于独立防火墙后，严格限制外部对 CGI 程序 imagemap.exe 的访问，并移除或重命名该 CGI 文件以阻断利用路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3380","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/739","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19566","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0951.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0951","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0951.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0951.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wrpp-w6hr-5mrv/GHSA-wrpp-w6hr-5mrv.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/mtesauro/owasp-wte/blob/e4c016caf67d59634f309f2a1feeed7dc9515abe/temp-projects/spikeproxy/contents/opt/owasp/spikeproxy/scan_database.db","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/imagemap.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0951.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1409.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1409.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1409.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1057","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1057.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1341","title":"Linux 内核 SLIP/PPP IP 数据包伪造漏洞","description":"Linux 2.3.18 之前版本及 2.2.13pre15 之前版本的内核中，当启用 SLIP 和 PPP 选项时存在 IP 数据包伪造漏洞。本地低权限用户可通过向 tty 设备发送 TIOCSETD ioctl 选项，将终端线路设置为 SLIP 模式，从而绕过内核的源地址校验机制伪造任意 IP 数据包。攻击者利用此漏洞可冒充其他主机发送伪造的网络流量，实施 IP 欺骗攻击，导致中间人攻击或拒绝服务等后果。该漏洞影响启用了 SLIP/PPP 模块的 Linux 系统，攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1341"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.3.18 及以上版本，或 2.2.13 正式版及以上版本，即可修复此漏洞。如无法升级内核，可卸载或禁用 SLIP 和 PPP 内核模块（modprobe -r slip ppp），并限制普通用户对 tty 设备 TIOCSETD ioctl 的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94061108411308&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7858","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1341"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1057.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1057.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0704","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0704.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0905","title":"Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0 IP选项零长度处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0 存在 IP 选项零长度拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向受影响的防火墙系统发送特制的零长度 IP 选项数据包，导致防火墙服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0905"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.040","remediation":"升级 Axent Raptor Firewall 至 6.0 以上版本，或安装厂商发布的安全补丁。如无法升级，可在防火墙配置中启用 IP 选项过滤规则，丢弃包含零长度 IP 选项的异常数据包。考虑到 Axent 已被 Symantec 收购且产品已停止维护，建议迁移至仍在安全支持周期内的替代防火墙产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1121","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/736","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19564","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d25d3aeab9dc76030f155f9e202a4a7c294f86bf/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0905.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0905","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0905.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0905.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5mcc-m9mr-95rg/GHSA-5mcc-m9mr-95rg.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/axent_raptor_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0905.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--918e494f-6310-4b0a-8c58-551af16b6512.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0704.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0766","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10772,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10790}}","description":"Microsoft Java 虚拟机（Microsoft JVM）存在沙箱逃逸漏洞。恶意 Java 小程序（applet）可利用该虚拟机的实现缺陷，绕过安全沙箱的限制，在用户浏览器加载该 applet 时于宿主机上执行任意系统命令。攻击者在网页中嵌入特制 applet 并诱导受害者访问即可触发，无需身份认证。该漏洞影响安装了 Microsoft JVM 的 Windows 系统（如 IE 浏览器环境），可导致远程代码执行，危害严重，CVSS 评分 9.3。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0766"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.830","remediation":"Microsoft Java Virtual Machine 已停止支持且不再提供更新，建议立即卸载 Microsoft VM 组件，迁移至受支持的 Java 运行时环境（如 Oracle Java 或 OpenJDK）。在浏览器中禁用 Java applet 执行功能，通过组策略或注册表禁止 Microsoft VM 的 javasrc.dll 加载。对于仍使用 Internet Explorer 的环境，在 Internet 选项→安全→自定义级别中将\"Java 权限\"设为\"禁用\"。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ240346","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/600","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-031","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0766.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0766","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0766.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/70f84d5684ed60f7a4d0750993d15c30e4fe3bbf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0766.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j3qp-hgf8-5gg9/GHSA-j3qp-hgf8-5gg9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0766.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000828.txt","https://github.com/mortada-albanna/data_science_notebooks/blob/12d819e5a22358f450a45c18f5ce3d9758566cba/COMP9321/Week3/Wrangling.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0691","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0691.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0895","title":"Check Point Firewall-1 LDAP属性访问限制不当漏洞","description":"Check Point Firewall-1 LDAP属性访问限制不当漏洞","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0895"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.810","remediation":"升级 Check Point Firewall-1 至最新受支持版本（当前为 Quantum Security Gateway R8x 系列），确保已应用所有安全补丁。在防火墙规则库中严格限制 LDAP（TCP 389）和 LDAPS（TCP 636）端口的访问源，仅允许受信管理服务器和认证服务器发起连接。禁用不必要的 LDAP 匿名查询功能，并在 LDAP 服务器对象中配置属性集访问控制列表（ACL），仅开放业务必需的属性字段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1117","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/725","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=19991020150002.21047.qmail%40tarjan.mediaways.net","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b9fb833e196fd08d699d3ef970b517d24cc12600/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0895.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0895","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0895.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0895.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0